name: Genacom Inc
overview:
Through the years Genacom has had the privilege of working with hundreds of clients in all stages of business and web development needs. We have a proven track record of delivering custom high quality solutions exceeding expectations to business owners from start-ups to corporations.

What once began as a Web Design company, nearly a decade ago has now emerged into a complete Business Development Organization comprised of a group of professionals dedicated to helping clients successfully meet their business goals.

The following companies were created as subsidiaries of Genacom with the intent to provide Business owners and Entrepreneurs all the tools they need to successfully manage their online business.
